</title>
<subSubSection id="B00791690E8AA25B6B225C9FCC908BC0" pageId="null" pageNumber="346" type="description">
<paragraph id="81C800532B649C1DF1DA937D448013AC" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="BC28879F986DCE661B5E8D5B9D9DBD1E" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Nardurus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="346" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lachenalii">
<emphasis id="F97ADD123167AF90404111DAF3931C86" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">F. Lachenalii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="FCDC0E59E4FB91A00844E51E0277ADA8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">
Hauptachse der Traube 3kantig; 
<normalizedToken id="68C9A33B84E3D3F1CC53B2B0FDB9FC89" originalValue="Ährchen" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Aehrchen</normalizedToken>
nur auf 2 
<normalizedToken id="E1C8843F9B7F40BF81D964967320A5B0" originalValue="Seitenflächen" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Seitenflaechen</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="3F9308ED085393784E8019EE58DEC7B3" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
deshalb einseitswendig; untere 
<normalizedToken id="926013091A2C1108FAA656926F16F07F" originalValue="Hüllspelze" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Huellspelze</normalizedToken>
1nervig, obere 3nervig; Deckspelzen spitz oder kurz begrannt.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="0D42A6643AD84F96380FF3750E82C8DA" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="59BDFF3505BEC7601995CDD556F4C0EF" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="73FEC303CFC08AA627F7316571E8C90C" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
bis Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F2668AA03C2A8EE136F9800F4673B1C7" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">
<emphasis id="8649ADBA77A545A57D68A8008D24272F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="970EEAFD1766DFF679D58EFAABC25ADD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">70:</emphasis>
Material aus Schleswig-Holstein (Wulff 1937a).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="141D41D5681A7AEFDD02B84021F258E3" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">
<emphasis id="FD4315392D3FA0F90A5310959925B402" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Standort.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="AC74792B6EEFFEFEBDCCFA04DB6AADAC" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Nardurus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="346" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lachenalii">
<emphasis id="9F175EB8F94BE9500E69678F0DF73EA6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">F. Lachenalii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1), jedoch auf kalkhaltigen 
<normalizedToken id="58492CB69E0C502D52D316E78D886D60" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Boeden</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F8B735831DE8101865C0BCCAB3F32F4C" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">
<emphasis id="54096489DCD61E7E668746B89F7EAAD6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
In 
<taxonomicName id="9EF8704B2953EF4A59BB2B09CDDB0FB9" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Europa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="346" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Europa</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="4C7FD82FEC38946AFCC21E9FFDE463DA" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="53D9F7600BD1846CB6C86DC2546B92E9" originalValue="Südengland" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Suedengland</normalizedToken>
, Belgien, Nancy, Rhonetal, 
<normalizedToken id="E428806CAA2FA9ACD08CA3D731BCC767" originalValue="Südtirol" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Suedtirol</normalizedToken>
(Rovereto), Balkanhalbinsel, Krim; Kleinasien, Kaukasus, Iran, 
<normalizedToken id="7DF9C780ABEF57C103D4240C7EA993D2" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis China; Nordwestafrika. - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="86095B62A1F609190290D3197941BB23" originalValue="Dép" pageId="null" pageNumber="346">Dep</normalizedToken>
. Ain, Savoyen, Genf, Wallis (in neuerer Zeit nicht mehr gefunden), Neuenburg; sehr selten.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
